      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-deploy-app/intro.bb4cf860.mp3",
      "narrationText": "是时候部署一个真实应用了！我们将从一个空仓库出发，三个简短步骤就让容器跑起来。",
      "audioDurationSec": 7.314286
    },
    {
